{"tid":570754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地去年推「限韓令」 韓旅遊收支逆差創新高","createTime":"2018-02-24T03:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T04:38:02.000Z","uid":53223,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c869349473a158262b18d1320a9651d0a81be76","tid":570754,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"韓國觀光公社數據顯示，去年赴韓旅遊的中國遊客人數為416.93萬人次，按年減48.3%。自中國政府3月起禁售赴韓團體遊產品，訪韓中國遊客人數急劇下滑，3月至12月，赴韓中國遊客按年銳減56.9%。<br />\n<br />\n去年韓國旅遊收支逆差達137.49億美元，是韓國旅遊收支自2001年以來連續17年出現逆差，並創下歷史新高。有分析指，受中國反制南韓部署「薩德」出台的「限韓令」，是韓國旅遊收支逆差創新高的主因。"},{"pid":"e10243c1a5e9688ef37a08726128c05069edaf11","tid":570754,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛優美開始</span>"},{"pid":"98451fa8fa8d7e091ae621bc4ffadb4737c1c17c","tid":570754,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e10243c1a5e9688ef37a08726128c05069edaf11","tid":570754,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛優美開始</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/115529_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F115529_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5337b25f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d78c3e93c9dea41d42a98e43ae3291701da44267","tid":570754,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e42d00d9d245ac6f744f073988e253c9b1bd8a2","tid":570754,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"少啲大陸人去韓國咪好囉 最後封閉哂個個國家都唔好去 自閉最好唔好搞人"},{"pid":"f355ba6d31017b49acb9d